extends ./layout.jade

block content

  section#slides

  section.quote.light
    div.container
      blockquote
        For 50 years, WWF has been protecting the future of nature. The world's leading
        conservation organization, WWF works in 100 countries and is supported by 1.2 million
        members in the United States and close to 5 million globally.

  section#sermons.green
    div.container
      h2
        i.fa.fa-clock-o.pre-icon
        | Diensten in de komende weken

      p
        | Elke zondag ochtend en middag is er een dienst in de Rehoboth kerk, waar iedereen welkom is.
        | Na de ochtenddienst kunt u meegenieten van de koffie, thee en fris.

      br

      table.table
        thead
          tr
            th Dienst
            th Tijd

        - for service in services
          tr
            td {{ service.title }}
            td {{ service.datetime|date:"f A - l d M" }}

  section#map

  //-
    section(startweek)

    section#family-banner
      .background(stellar-background="0.8")

      .container.text-center.light
        h4
          span.larger 300
          | jonge en oude leden
          | die samen een frisse gemeente vormen.

    section(calendar)

    section(contact)
